A PUBLIC SERVICE, AND NOW HOPES
THAT "ONE SMALL STEP" CAN HELP

17:18.237 --> 17:25.244
END WHAT HE CALLS THE "CULTURE
OF CONTEMPT" THAT IS TEARING
APART THE COUNTRY.
>> Isay: THE SITUATION IS SO BAD

17:25.310 --> 17:32.985
THAT, YOU KNOW, IF-- IF THE
CULTURE OF CONTEMPT WINS--
