WHO DISAGREE POLITICALLY, TO PUT

24:38.610 --> 24:43.215
THEM FACE-TO-FACE FOR 50
MINUTES.
IT'S NOT TO TALK ABOUT POLITICS;
IT'S JUST TO TALK ABOUT YOUR

24:43.281 --> 24:50.922
LIVES.
